 history from a contemporary point of view.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCanadian poetry (English)xHistory and criticismx20th centuryxKanadaxEnglisch. 0aCanadian poetryxHistory and criticismx20th century. 0aCanadian poetryy20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aEsthétisme (Littérature)xInfluence. 0aModernisme (Littérature)xCanada. 0aPoésie canadienne-anglaisexHistoire et critiquex20e siècle. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Canadian.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077356209740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773562097423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773562097/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles